John K. Morgan  Director, WESCO International, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 6 different industries.See Board Relationships63$220,429
Background

		Mr. John K. Morgan served as Chief Executive Officer and President of Zep, Inc. since October 2007 until June 26, 2015. Mr. Morgan held several positions at Acuity Brands from 2001 to 2007. He served as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Acuity Lighting Group Inc., subsidiary of Acuity Brands Inc., since August 2005. He served as Chief Executive Officer of Acuity Specialty Products. He served as the President of Zep, Inc. from July 2007 to November 2007. He ... served as an Executive Vice President of Acuity Brands Inc from July 2007 to October 2007.  He served as the Chief Executive Officer and President of Acuity Brands Lighting, a subsidiary of Acuity Brands Inc. from August 2, 2005. He served as President and Chief Development Officer of Acuity Brands Inc., parent company of Acuity Lighting Group, Inc. since January 21, 2004. He served as a Senior Executive Vice President and the Chief Operating Officer of Acuity Brands Inc., since June 2002 and also an Executive Vice President from December 2001 to June 2002. Mr. Morgan served as President of Holophane at National Service Industries Inc. since June 2000. He served as Executive Vice President of Sales and Marketing of Lithonia Lighting Group from 1999 to 2001. He served as the Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer of Zep Inc., from October 2007 until June 2015. He joined Lithonia Lighting in 1977 and held a variety of senior management positions prior to 1999. He has been a Director at Zep Inc. since July 2007 and WESCO International, Inc. since March 31, 2008. He has been a Director of LSI Industries Inc. since April 20,2016.Read Full Background




