John K. Morgan 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer at ZEP INC, John K. Morgan  made $2,397,874 in total compensation.  Of this total $645,000 was received as a salary, $352,712 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $1,186,088 was awarded as stock and $214,074 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2014 fiscal year. 


